#: of numpy.polynomial.laguerre.lagsub:35
msgid ""
"Unlike multiplication, division, etc., the difference of two Laguerre series "
"is a Laguerre series (without having to \"reproject\" the result onto the "
"basis set) so subtraction, just like that of \"standard\" polynomials, is "
"simply \"component-wise.\""
msgstr ""

